                <mxCell id="lane-g" value="G · noodle-domain   (Agent Protocol content-semantic types — used by downstream consumers, not in the proxy data path)" style="swimlane;startSize=24;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;horizontal=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
